				<li>A: The metric check can be conducted (a)utomatically.</li>
				<li>Q: The metric check can be conducted (q)uickly by human
					inspection.</li>
				<li>D: The metric check would be (d)ifficult to conduct by human
					inspection.</li>
			</ul>
